title: Placement Student Interview
Application Type: I interviewed at York Hills Centre for Children, Youth and Families
Interview Descriptions: Very smooth. The whole process was great, very pleasant. The interviewers were very respectful and pleasant. There was humour in the interview too. They got back to me exactly when they said they would. The whole process was seamless and relatively quick. They were very understanding of my course’s requirements.
Interview Questions: Q. What do you do for self care during sessions? Q. How do you manage deadlines?
